	* date-memoize/Rakefile, date-memoize/ext,
	  date-memoize/ext/date_fast.c, date-memoize/ext/extconf.rb,
	  date-memoize/lib/date/fast.rb, date-memoize/lib/date/memoize.rb,
	  date-memoize/test/extension_test.rb:
	  
	  Add date_fast C extension and tests. Initial implementation speeds
	  up the following Date singleton methods by providing implementations
	  in C:
	  
	  * Date::civil_to_jd
	  * Date::jd_to_civil
	  * Date::jd_to_ajd
	  * Date::new
	  
	  Benchmarks are showing somewhere around an 80% gain in creation
	  performance
	  when using Date::new, Date::civil, Date::jd.

